==========================================================================
RUNTIME DEPENDENCIES (NOT DISTRIBUTED)
==========================================================================

Nexus can optionally load Coq-verified runtime modules at startup.
These modules are NOT part of the Nexus distribution:

- meta_kernel_rules.dll — 5 meta rules (Coq verified via Recursor Theory)
- constructive_rules.dll — Constructive logic rules (Coq extracted)
  Underlying Coq proofs reside in the user's existing D:/synapse/ installation.

These DLLs are loaded dynamically at runtime if present.
Nexus runs without them (degraded mode).

